            <br />
            <div class="one-half" id="train" style="width:55%">
                <p>It is a well-known fact that English is a native language for over 350 million people around the world. However, the total English-speaking population, including users of English as a second language, is estimated at well over 1 billion. This makes English the most widely used language outside of native-speaking countries, as well as being the official language for a number of major world organisations. Put simply, the ability to speak and do business in English will expand your horizons to all corners of the earth in this age of rapid globalization.</p>
                <p>Pace Training and Consultancy specializes in a number of key areas of language training.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="one-half last" style="width: auto;background-color:rgba(4, 53, 114, 1);padding:25px;border-radius:25px;color:white;">
                Intensive Courses (1-2 days):
                <ul class="unordered">
                    <li>Meeting Techniques</li>
                    <li>Professional Writing Skills</li>
                    <li>Presentation Skills (ideal for university students)</li>
                </ul>
                Multi-session intensive courses (1 month / 8 sessions):
                <ul class="unordered">
                    <li>Fast Acquisition of Spoken English (FASE)</li>
                </ul>
                Long-running courses (6 -12 weeks):
                <ul class="unordered">
                    <li>General and Business English for all levels</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
