                            <h4><i class="icon-megaphone-1"></i>Presentation Skills</h4>                            
                            <p><strong>Required qualifications:</strong> General English level of Intermediate or higher.</p>
                            <p><strong>Number of participants:</strong> Open</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="two-third last">
                            <p>Boost your presentation skills and blast your audience.</p>
                            <p>In this one-day course, we show you some of the worst habits in public speaking. We will then demonstrate some much more practical and dynamic methods. </p>
                            <ul class="unordered">
                                <li>How can you warm up your audience?</li>
                                <li>How can you keep them interested?</li>
                                <li>How do you direct their attention to the specific key points of your presentation?</li>
                                <li>How should your slide show look?</li>                                
                            </ul>
                            <p>Some pretty cool tricks!</p>
                            <p>We will also teach you how to boost your confidence even further for that all-important day.</p>
                        </div>
